-- ============================================================
-- GENEALOGY PERSON: Mala
-- Generated: 2026-01-10
-- ============================================================
-- LIMITED INFORMATION: Mestre Mala is documented as one of the three
-- original co-founders of Associação de Capoeira 3 Amigos (1974) alongside
